## Summary
This documentation details the Clevertap Event Streaming integration with Amplitude, allowing event data to be sent from Amplitude to CleverTap for enhanced user engagement and analytics. The setup requires CleverTap credentials (Account ID, Passcode, Region) and configuration in Amplitude's Data Destinations to map user identities and select which events to stream.

